                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Once per day, a huitz\u2019plina can spend a Resolve Point to receive a hazy vision related to the outcome of an event, goal, or activity as far as a day into the future. This otherwise functions as augury with a 100% chance of successfully receiving a meaningful reply.",
