                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Once per day, after a huitz\u2019plina takes the total defense action and before the start of their next turn, they can take a reaction to launch a barrage of spines in a 20-foot spread centered on themselves. Every other creature in the area must succeed at a Reflex save (DC = 10 + half the huitz\u2019plina\u2019s level + the huitz\u2019plina\u2019s Constitution modifier) or take piercing damage equal to three times the huitz\u2019plina\u2019s level; a successful save halves this damage.",
